Oddbins Managing Director Fails in Purchase Attempt, Times Says

-- B y   N a n d i n i   S u k u m a r
-- 
2011-04-23T15:20:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-23/oddbins-managing-director-fails-in-purchase-attempt-times-says.html
Simon Baile, managing director of
Oddbins Properties Ltd., has failed in an attempt to buy back
the unprofitable U.K. wine retailer from administrators, the
London-based  Times  reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nandini Sukumar in London at 
 nsukumar@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
